<hymn_number>1028</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 mạfysẖ gẖyrk ystḥq .. kl tsbyḥạty
 mạfysẖ gẖyrk ạ̉hdyh .. kl trnymạty
 mạfysẖ gẖyrk ạ̉dyh .. ʿmry wḥyạty
 mạfysẖ gẖyrk ạ̉htf lyh .. fy kl ạ̉wqạty
 (hạfḍl ạ̉sbḥ kl ʿmry .. rby wạhtf lyk
 hạfḍl ạ̉gẖny bkl qlby .. dạymaⁿạ whạʿlyk)2
 (wqt frḥy .. wwqt ḥzny
 wqt ḍʿfy .. wwqt nṣry)2
 wạ̉nạ dạymaⁿạ bạlạqy yạ rby .. kl kfạyty fyk</lyrics>
<title>mạfysẖ gẖyrk ystḥq</title>
</song>